			length	width	depth
	1 temporal dimension
		tek yönde hissedilen bir boyut
		geri dönemeyiz
		bu yüzden seçim yapmak zor
		seçim yoksa herşey ihtimal dahilinde.

	The superstring theory predicts that there are nine dimensions of space. 
	Of these, three are our three-dimensional space, 
		expressed as length, width, and height. 
	The remaining six dimensions are folded and compactified very tightl, and we cannot perceive them directly.
	https://www.questseans.com/space-cadet/2018/7/10/10-dimensions-of-reality

